name: Sprint
description: SWP is the heart and soul of the Sprint project. As a utility token, it serves a multitude of purposes within the Sprint ecosystem. It's not just a digital asset; it's a key that unlocks a variety of features and opportunities. Whether you're participating in Move-to-Earn activities, staking in the DeFi zones, or trading in the NFT Marketplace, SWP is the currency that fuels your actions. Its versatility and integration into the platform make it an essential part of the user experience.
